acia: Land of Transylvania, Cornerstone of Ancient Eastern Europe|publisher=University Press of America|pages=75|isbn=076184466X}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Hedrick2009>{{cite journal|doi=10.1038/hdy.2009.77|pmid=19603061|title=Wolf of a different colour|journal=Heredity|volume=103|issue=6|pages=435\u2013436|year=2009|last1=Hedrick|first1=P. W.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Heraldry>{{cite book |last=Fox-Davies|first= Arthur Charles |author-link=Arthur Charles Fox-Davies |last2= Johnston|first2= Graham |date=2004 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0EBiwcy4x5EC&pg=PA196 |title=A Complete Guide to Heraldry |publisher=Kessinger Publishing |pp=196\u2013197 |isbn=1-4179-0630-8 |access-date=2015-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611022224/https://books.google.com/books?id=0EBiwcy4x5EC&pg=PA196 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=HolyLand>{{cite book|last=Qumsiyeh|first=Mazin B.|year=1996|title=Mammals of the Holy Land|publisher=Texas Tech University Press|pages=146\u2013148|isbn=089672364X}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Iacolina2010>{{cite journal|doi=10.1016/j.mambio.2010.02.004|title=Y-chromosome microsatellite variation in Italian wolves: A contribution to the study of wolf-dog hybridization patterns|journal=Mammalian Biology - Zeitschrift f\u00fcr S\u00e4ugetierkunde|volume=75|issue=4|page=341|year=2010|last1=Iacolina|first1=Laura|last2=Scandura|first2=Massimo|last3=Gazzola|first3=Andrea|last4=Cappai|first4=Nadia|last5=Capitani|first5=Claudia|last6=Mattioli|first6=Luca|last7=Vercillo|first7=Francesca|last8=Apollonio|first8=Marco}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Ishiguro2009>{{cite journal|doi=10.2108/zsj.26.765 |pmid=19877836|title=Mitochondrial DNA Analysis of the Japanese Wolf (Canis Lupus Hodophilax ''Temminck'', 1839) and Comparison with Representative Wolf and Domestic Dog Haplotypes|journal=Zoological Science|volume=26|issue=11|pages=765\u201370 |year=2009|last1=Ishiguro|first1=Naotaka |last2=Inoshima|first2=Yasuo|last3=Shigehara|first3=Nobuo}}</ref>